14 游戏作战 | 加速「知识原始积累」，享受知识复利

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appD8YSmEyz7255/a_5bfcf243f0c3d_ulmk3WTc

<p style="white-space: normal;"><strong style="color: rgb(0, 176, 240); font-size: 20px;"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;;">读了很多书，但是都忘掉了，读书的意义在哪里？</span></strong><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><blockquote style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px 1em; color: rgb(106, 115, 125); border-left: 0.25em solid rgb(223, 226, 229); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: auto;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; box-sizing: border-box;">忘掉了里面经典的话语，</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; box-sizing: border-box;">忘掉了故事的经过，</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">忘掉了作者的感悟。</p></blockquote><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: auto;">一年看似读了几十本书，但是，就像水流过了石头，风一吹，太阳一晒，什么都没有留下。那么，读书的意义到底是什么？</p><p style="white-space: normal;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appDlhUKBqJ1468/image/ueditor/72750400_1543301482.png" alt="" style="box-sizing: content-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-b