<p style="white-space: normal;"><strong style="color: rgb(0, 176, 240); font-size: 20px;"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;;">读了很多书，但是都忘掉了，读书的意义在哪里？</span></strong><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><blockquote style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px 1em; color: rgb(106, 115, 125); border-left: 0.25em solid rgb(223, 226, 229); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: auto;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; box-sizing: border-box;">忘掉了里面经典的话语，</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; box-sizing: border-box;">忘掉了故事的经过，</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">忘掉了作者的感悟。</p></blockquote><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: auto;">一年看似读了几十本书，但是，就像水流过了石头，风一吹，太阳一晒，什么都没有留下。那么，读书的意义到底是什么？</p><p style="white-space: normal;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appDlhUKBqJ1468/image/ueditor/72750400_1543301482.png" alt="" style="box-sizing: content-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);">把「读书」换成「学习」，也是一样扎心。学了很多知识，但是忘掉了，学习的意义在哪里？</span></p><blockquote style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px 1em; color: rgb(106, 115, 125); border-left: 0.25em solid rgb(223, 226, 229); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: auto;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; box-sizing: border-box;">忘掉了高考前挑灯夜战、刻苦到心疼才换来的「知识」；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; box-sizing: border-box;">忘掉了大学里老教授白发苍苍、勤勤恳恳传授的智慧；</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">忘掉了书本和网络上浏览、收藏、转发的无数干货；</p></blockquote><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);">不是读书和学习没有意义，而是，你缺乏一个正确的「读完不忘」、「学完不忘」的科学记忆系统。</span><span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>缺乏一个正确的知识内化方法，就会出现「假学习」、「低品质努力」的情况：</p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="margin-bottom: 16px; width: 649.797px; padding-left: 2em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: auto;"><li><p>虚：学习时「收获满满」，应用时「大脑空空」？</p></li><li><p>贪：满足于一年读了n本书，最后只有自己知道其实连书名都没记住？</p></li><li><p>蛮：死记硬背使蛮力，看到考题只记得「曾经看过」，其他都忘光了？</p></li><li><p>痛：看到孩子重蹈「死记硬背」「题海战术」的覆辙，父母除了心痛却束手无策？</p></li><li><p>假：笔记记了一大堆，「自我感动」之后该忘还是忘？……</p></li></ul><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;;">我们缺乏的不是努力，而是可以积累的努力；我们最缺乏的不是在「死记硬背」上的低效努力，而是在「如何科学记忆」方法论上的一点点努力！如果你想解决以上所有问题，那你迫切需要这次的21天知识内化训练营！</span><br/></p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="margin-bottom: 16px; width: 649.797px; padding-left: 2em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: auto;"><li><p>对于记忆，不再使蛮力「死记硬背」，而是用科学的认知规律「智取」</p></li><li><p>对于学习，不再是无聊的重复，而是设计游戏，让学习变得有趣</p></li><li><p>对于遗忘，不再是一些记忆技巧的堆砌，而是全流程的系统解决方案</p></li></ul><h3 style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.25; font-size: 1.25em; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 176, 240);"><br/></span></h3><h3 style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.25; font-size: 1.25em; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 176, 240);">学习完15节后，你将获得</span></h3><h4 style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.25; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 176, 240);">1个「学完不忘」的知识内化系统</span></h4><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="margin-bottom: 16px; width: 649.797px; padding-left: 2em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: auto;"><li><p>建立「读书-笔记-记忆-输出」的「读书闭环」</p></li><li><p>交付精心打磨的整体学习解决方案</p></li><li><p>让学习成为行云流水的「学习流水线」</p></li></ul><h4 style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.25; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 176, 240);">2套「超级大脑」的强化升级方案</span></h4><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="margin-bottom: 16px; width: 649.797px; padding-left: 2em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: auto;"><li><p>大脑健身，科学记忆，让「内脑」更强健：学习之后大脑不再「空空如也」，而是「硕果累累」</p></li><li><p>大脑升级，善用利器，用「外脑」更轻松：给你一个随身的大脑移动硬盘，随取随用，一次学习，终生受用</p></li></ul><h4 style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.25; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; text-size-adjust: auto;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 176, 240);">3个「效率翻倍」的个人管理方案</span></h4><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="margin-bottom: 16px; width: 649.797px; padding-left: 2em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; font-size: 15px; text-size-adjust: auto;"><li><p>「书到用时找不着」？建立知识管理方案，知识可检索，努力可积累</p></li><li><p>「没有时间读书学习」？为学习者订制时间管理方案，碎片时间变废为宝</p></li><li><p>「学习三天打鱼两天晒网」？设计学习者的自我激励方案，在游戏中轻松成长&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p></li></ul><h3 style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.25; font-size: 1.25em; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 176, 240);"><br/></span></h3><h3 style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.25; font-size: 1.25em; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 176, 240);">训练营学什么？</span></h3><p style="white-space: normal;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appDlhUKBqJ1468/image/ueditor/77194000_1543302333.png" title=".png" alt="知识内化分销版课程表.png"/></p><h3 style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.25; font-size: 1.25em; color: rgb(36, 41, 46); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Segoe UI&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, &#39;Apple Color Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Emoji&#39;, &#39;Segoe UI Symbol&#39;; text-size-adjust: auto; text-align: center;"><s